The `policyBase * 1.1 + PROCESSING_FEE` line has a magic number `1.1` (10% first-insurance surcharge). I can extract it as a named constant for clarity. Also, the inline comment about epsilon could be a named helper.

Let me extract the `1.1` magic number into a named constant since it represents the "first insurance surcharge" semantically.

